{"by":"habosa","id":47774690,"kids":[47775408,47777409],"parent":47728662,"text":"I went to Spain as a teenager and saw Guernica in person. It was the first painting to ever really have an effect on me. It&#x27;s stunning. A perfect example of how art can transmit a message between people across time and space, I just knew that I was feeling how Picasso wanted me to feel.<p>If you have the chance to see this painting you should, no website can do it justice (although this is a very nice try).","time":1776227361,"type":"comment"}